# ---- Concept hierarchy ----
# Concepts that operators implement, organized via is_subclass_of.
# The family query traverses (op)-[:implements]->(concept)-[:is_subclass_of]->(family).

Min-Max Scaling is subclass of Scaling
Standard Scaling is subclass of Scaling
Robust Scaling is subclass of Scaling
Normalization is subclass of Scaling
Quantile Transformation is subclass of Scaling
Power Transformation is subclass of Scaling

One-Hot Encoding is subclass of Encoding
Label Encoding is subclass of Encoding
Ordinal Encoding is subclass of Encoding

Support Vector Classification is subclass of Support Vector Machine
Linear Support Vector Classification is subclass of Support Vector Machine

AdaBoost is subclass of Ensemble
Extra Trees is subclass of Ensemble
Gradient Boosting is subclass of Ensemble
Random Forest is subclass of Ensemble
Random Trees Embedding is subclass of Ensemble

Bernoulli Naive Bayes is subclass of Naive Bayes
Gaussian Naive Bayes is subclass of Naive Bayes
Multinomial Naive Bayes is subclass of Naive Bayes

Decision Tree Classification is subclass of Decision Tree

K-Nearest Neighbors is subclass of Nearest Neighbors

Linear Discriminant Analysis is subclass of Discriminant Analysis
Quadratic Discriminant Analysis is subclass of Discriminant Analysis

Multi-Layer Perceptron is subclass of Neural Network

Passive-Aggressive Classification is subclass of Linear Model
Stochastic Gradient Descent is subclass of Linear Model

Simple Imputation is subclass of Imputation

Fast ICA is subclass of Decomposition
Kernel PCA is subclass of Decomposition
Principal Component Analysis is subclass of Decomposition
Truncated SVD is subclass of Decomposition

Feature Agglomeration is subclass of Agglomeration

RBF Sampling is subclass of Kernel Approximation
Nystroem Approximation is subclass of Kernel Approximation

Polynomial Features is subclass of Feature Generator

Percentile Feature Selection is subclass of Feature Selector
K-Best Feature Selection is subclass of Feature Selector

Train-Test Split is subclass of Model Selection
K-Fold Cross-Validation is subclass of Model Selection
Stratified K-Fold Cross-Validation is subclass of Model Selection

